@C airgenome_a1_summary_0 = OS-genome scanner — projects Mac+remote vitals onto a 6-axis hexagon (60-byte genome), accumulates patterns, detects anomalies. Rebuild v2 (M0~M6 milestones) shipped 2026-04-14, post-archive v1 freeze. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [7]
  => summary of axis a1 (project identity)
  |> airgenome (read-only absorption 2026-04-27)

