@C AIRGENOME_AG6_RULE_21 = Mac Compute ZERO when any remote (ubu|htz|hetzner) active. Enforced by modules/filters/process/compute.hexa (30s launchd com.airgenome.compute-filter). TERM 3s → KILL leftover. WHITELIST persists. Mac = orchestration/UI/dispatch only. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [11*REPO_INVARIANT]
  => repo invariant (ossified 2026-04-12, level ⛔⛔⛔)
  |> airgenome/rules/airgenome.json id=AG6

@C AIRGENOME_AG7_RULE_22 = real-time load balancing on infra_state.json (60s fresh). Score = cpu_free·w_cpu + ram_free·w_ram + gpu_free·w_gpu + lan_bonus. Weights per task_type: gpu_heavy(1,2,5), cpu_heavy(5,2,0), realtime_gpu(1,2,3+lan30), io_heavy(1,3,0+lan20). Mac excluded under AG6. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [11*REPO_INVARIANT]
  => repo invariant (ossified 2026-04-12, level ⛔⛔)
  |> airgenome/rules/airgenome.json id=AG7

@C AIRGENOME_AG8_RULE_23 = ssh_gate enforcement: 4-slot semaphore per-host, command filter (DENY: rm -rf /, reboot, shutdown, dd, mkfs, chmod 777 → exit 2; WARN: sudo, pkill, killall, systemctl stop/restart), passive metric piggyback (loadavg+meminfo per call), reinterpret actions (cpu_idle→fill_queue, ram_critical→drop_caches, cpu_overload→renice). 16 files / 60 ssh calls migrated. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [11*REPO_INVARIANT]
  => repo invariant (ossified 2026-04-12, level ⛔⛔)
  |> airgenome/rules/airgenome.json id=AG8

@C AIRGENOME_AG10_RULE_24 = Claude-Code harness-UI layer (hooks/skills/settings.json hooks/MCP approval/update-config/CLAUDE.md/init) is FORBIDDEN. All policy lives in two hexa-only SSOTs: nexus/rules/airgenome.json (AG*) + hexa-lang/gate/enforcement_registry.json (H-*). Single bootstrap exception: one global UserPromptSubmit hook → hexa entry.hexa dispatcher. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [11*REPO_INVARIANT]
  => repo invariant (ossified 2026-04-21, level ⛔⛔)
  |> airgenome/rules/airgenome.json id=AG10

@C AIRGENOME_AG5_FILTER_DEF_25 = "filter" name reserved for raw-bytes → byte-reencoding transforms only (real-time hot-path speed/memory/IO improvement). Lossless or labeled-lossy required, encode/decode round-trip or query-latency measurable. Sweepers, dedup, gzip, cron, sync, watcher, throttle, kickstart use distinct names (compress/guard/dedup/sync/watcher). :: omega_cycle_airgenome [11*REPO_INVARIANT]
  => repo invariant (ossified 2026-04-11, level 🔴)
  |> airgenome/rules/airgenome.json id=AG5

@C AIRGENOME_HARVEST_PIPELINE_26 = harvest top-N=30 ps procs (CPU-sorted) → 60B genome JSONL line / row → forge/genomes.ring (cap MAX_LINES=5000 ≈2-3MB, head-half rotate). DIFF_THRESHOLD=10 per axis, sigdiff_score = count(|curr_axis - prev_axis| > 10) over 6 axes → anomaly score. EMA: alpha=0.1 IIR (curr·1+prev·9)/10. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]
  => structural fact (M4 pipeline)
  |> airgenome/modules/harvest.hexa lines 22-26 + 211-245

@C AIRGENOME_LABEL_PIPELINE_27 = label runs label_rules.jsonl SSOT against last 1000 ring lines. Built-in rules: CPU_SPIKE (axis 0 > 80), MEM_LEAK (1 > 50), FORK_BOMB (cpu>50 AND ram>20), IO_STORM (axis 5 > 50), GPU_HOG (axis 2 > 80), REMOTE_UBU_CPU/REMOTE_HTZ_CPU (host-scoped axis 0 > 85). Output: forge/labeled_anomaly.jsonl with optional host preserved. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]
  => structural fact (M5 + M11d)
  |> airgenome/modules/label.hexa + airgenome/config/label_rules.jsonl

@C AIRGENOME_FORECAST_PIPELINE_28 = forecast applies Holt's linear (ALPHA=BETA=50/100) to last 5000 ring lines, top-20 PIDs × 2 axes (cpu,ram). 1-step-ahead prediction = level + h·trend, written to forge/forecast.jsonl. self-test: linear series 0..80 → predict 90 with MAE<15%; flat series MAE=0%. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*PROBE_RUN]
  => simulator-verified (synthetic series within self_test)
  |> airgenome/modules/forecast.hexa lines 17-23, 217-299

@C AIRGENOME_PREDICTIVE_THROTTLE_29 = Mac self-protection (M14): sample → forge/throttle_history.jsonl (last 30 samples ≈30min @60s) → Holt 1-step pred. Triggers if pred_cpu>80 OR pred_ram>75. Action = launchctl bootout non-whitelisted com.airgenome.* (LaunchAgent → auto-recover at next StartInterval). TTL=90s. NO kill. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]
  => structural fact (predictive guard, AG6 reinforcement)
  |> airgenome/modules/predictive_throttle.hexa lines 1-23, 150-194

@C AIRGENOME_DISPATCH_SCORING_30 = score_compute = cpu_free + ram_free - 20·load (clamp 0..100). score_gpu = ((100-util)·2 + vram_free·2)/4 (active only). score_heavy = score_compute + thread_bonus (≥16t:+20, ≥8t:+10). Tie-break: ubu > ubu2 > htz > mac (LAN+GPU first, LAN compute next, remote last). AG6 gate zeros mac when any remote active. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]
  => structural fact (M3 scoring)
  |> airgenome/modules/dispatch.hexa lines 41-211

@C AIRGENOME_GENOME_MERGE_31 = M11c: 3 host rings → unified ring. jq -c '. + {host:"<H>", pid:("<H>." + (.pid|tostring))}' avoids PID collision. self-test: 3×2 lines per host with overlapping pid=1 → 6 unique pids. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]
  => structural fact (multi-host pipeline)
  |> airgenome/modules/genome_merge.hexa

@C AIRGENOME_PROBE_REMOTES_32 = probe ssh -o ConnectTimeout=5 -o BatchMode=yes ubu/ubu2/hetzner — extracts load + ram + (ubu only) nvidia-smi gpu_util + vram. Empty CSV → status=offline. ubu schema = 6 fields, htz/ubu2 schema = 4 fields (no GPU). Atomic write to $NEXUS/infra_state.json via .tmp + mv. :: omega_cycle_airgenome [10*]
